sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant xterm as xterm.js
    participant Hook as useTerminal
    participant Bridge as tauri-bridge
    participant Cmd as terminal.rs
    participant PTY as PtyHandle
    participant Shell as Shell Process

    Note over User,Shell: Session Creation
    Hook->>Bridge: createTerminalSession()
    Bridge->>Cmd: invoke("create_terminal_session")
    Cmd->>PTY: PtyHandle::spawn("/bin/zsh", 24, 80)
    PTY->>Shell: fork + exec shell
    PTY-->>Cmd: (PtyHandle, PtyReader)
    Cmd->>Cmd: Store in SessionMap
    Cmd->>Cmd: spawn pty_read_loop thread
    Cmd-->>Bridge: { session_id }
    Bridge-->>Hook: session_id
    Hook->>Hook: Setup xterm.onData + onResize

    Note over User,Shell: Keystroke Flow
    User->>xterm: Types "ls -la\n"
    xterm->>Hook: onData(bytes)
    Hook->>Bridge: writeToPty(sid, bytes)
    Bridge->>Cmd: invoke("write_to_pty")
    Cmd->>PTY: handle.write(bytes)
    PTY->>Shell: write to master fd

    Note over User,Shell: Output Flow
    Shell->>PTY: writes output to slave
    PTY->>Cmd: pty_read_loop reads 4096 bytes
    Cmd->>Bridge: emit("pty:data", {sid, data})
    Bridge->>Hook: onPtyData callback
    Hook->>xterm: terminal.write(decoded text)
    xterm->>User: Renders output
